flowchart LR
    Flow["Automated flow"] --> Pause["Pause before a gated action"]
    Pause --> Request["ApprovalRequest\naction type · summary · risk · payload"]
    Request --> Human["Human reviews the request"]
    Human -->|approve| Resume["Resume and execute"]
    Human -->|reject| Stop["Do not execute"]
    Resume --> Decision["ApprovalDecision\napprover + reason"]
    Stop --> Decision

    style Pause fill:#f3e5f5,stroke:#7b1fa2
    style Request fill:#e3f2fd,stroke:#1976d2
    style Human fill:#e8f5e9,stroke:#388e3c
    style Decision fill:#fff8e1,stroke:#f9a825
